<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DEVSHOP 회원가입</title>
    <style>
        /* ... (이전의 구조적 스타일 유지) ... */
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f8f8f8; }
        .header-top { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 10px 20px; }
        .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; }
        .right-menu a { margin-left: 10px; text-decoration: none; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 50px auto; padding: 40px; background-color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .register-box { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 30px; }
        .title { font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .input-group { margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .input-group input { width: 100%; padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
        .checkbox-group { margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .agreement-item { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-left: 20px; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 5px; }
        .required { color: red; }
        .btn-register { width: 100%; padding: 15px; background-color: #ccc; border: none; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 30px; font-weight: bold; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<header class="header-top">
    <div class="logo">DEVSHOP</div>
    <div class="right-menu">
        <a href="#">고객센터</a>
        <a href="#">마이페이지</a>
        <a href="/">로그인</a>
        <span class="menu-icon">☰</span>
    </div>
</header>

<div class="container">
    <div class="register-box">
        <h2 class="title">회원가입</h2>

        <form action="/users/join" method="post">
            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="email" style="display: block; font-weight: bold;">이메일 주소</label>
                <input type="text" id="username" name="username" placeholder="예) sample@dev.com">
            </div>

            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="password" style="display: block; font-weight: bold;">비밀번호 *</label>
                <input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력하세요">
                <small style="color: #999; display: block; margin-top: 5px;">영문, 숫자, 특수문자 중 2가지 이상을 조합하여 10자~16자 이내로 입력하세요.</small>
            </div>

            <div class="checkbox-group">
                <label>
                    <input type="checkbox" name="agreeAll" id="agreeAll" value="Y">
                    **모두 동의합니다**
                </label>
                <small style="color: #999; display: block; margin-left: 20px;">선택 약관에 대한 동의를 포함하여 모두 동의합니다.</small>
                <hr>

                <div class="agreement-item">
                    <label>
                        <input type="checkbox" name="requiredTerms1" value="Y">
                        [<span class="required">필수</span>] 이용약관 동의
                    </label>
                    <a href="#" style="color: #666; text-decoration: underline;">전문보기</a>
                </div>
                <div class="agreement-item">
                    <label>
                        <input type="checkbox" name="requiredTerms2" value="Y">
                        [<span class="required">필수</span>] 개인정보 수집 및 이용 동의
                    </label>
                    <a href="#" style="color: #666; text-decoration: underline;">전문보기</a>
                </div>
                <div class="agreement-item">
                    <label>
                        <input type="checkbox" name="marketingAgree" value="Y">
                        [선택] 이메일/문자 수신 및 마케팅 동의
                    </label>
                    <a href="#" style="color: #666; text-decoration: underline;">동의안함</a>
                </div>
                <div class="agreement-item">
                    <label>
                        <input type="checkbox" name="eventAgree" value="Y">
                        [선택] 상품정보 수신 및 이벤트 동의
                    </label>
                    <a href="#" style="color: #666; text-decoration: underline;">동의안함</a>
                </div>

            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="btn-register">본인인증 후 회원가입 하기</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>

<footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="#">회사소개</a> |
        <a href="#">이용약관</a> |
        <a href="#">개인정보처리방침</a> |
        <a href="#">사업자정보확인</a>
    </div>
    <p>Created By HR | All Right Reserved</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>